Camoflage::

She came bounding up through the forest and running up to the maximal 
base.  She had been trapped in a quintesson trap for sometime. Only 
now it had released her and she was free to go back to her friends. 
She was after all, a fox pup.  She didn't have a care in the world 
except for telling her trainer BlackFang that she was OK and that she 
wanted to go back to training with him. He was her best friend as far 
as she was concerned. "BLACKFANG!!! I"M HOME!!! I"M HOME!!!"  She ran 
right up to the front doors of the maximal base and saw a bot laying 
there at the doors. She didn't know what the matter was, but even in 
her young mind, she knew something was wrong. She opened up an 
emergency channel. It broadcast over all frequencies and the base 
intercom. "HEY GUYS! It's me, Camoflage. I'm home. And there is a bot 
here in trouble out here. Hey guys, open up. I'm hungry too."
